videos.headline: In transition, Kasey Hill makes a nice pass to allow Kevarrius Hayes to lay it in
Justin Leon comes out of nowhere for the put back slam
Canyon Barry misses an easy dunk and his father Rick Barry has a great reaction
Przemek Karnowski scores and gets fouled for the Bulldogs
